PWR wins all six; mean Δ over rigid = +0.066.  Affine alone barely
moves the needle on most subjects (+0.01) — the gain is dominated by
the PWR stage.  See
`code/sessions/08_surface_vascular_match/figures/compare_methods_v2_summary.png`.

## When to re-run

The cache is invalidated by changes upstream of registration:

* CZ or HCR top surface refit (delete cached entries in
  `dev_code/cached_surfaces/` to force re-registration with new
  surfaces);
* `sxy` re-estimate (e.g., a new ROI-area or landmark fit);
* CZ outline TIFF (`*seg-mask-outline.tif`) changes.

To rebuild from scratch for all benchmark subjects:
```
python /root/capsule/code/dev_code/surface_registration_v2.py
```

